{"tid":2331204,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王嘉爾深V熱貼Jessi辣翻！　JYP合體宣美《NOBODY》網嗨喊：歐巴","createTime":"2020-12-18T14:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T15:38:29.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"246757c7e9376f6d2aa2e838aef8ee31a1654d0c","tid":2331204,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ZNF4NDCrTM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_ZNF4NDCrTM&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=63d7aa99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_ZNF4NDCrTM</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓電視台年末慶典之一的KBS《歌謠大祝祭》18日正式播出，今年依舊有許多話題舞台。包括GOT7成員Jackson（王嘉爾）和「霸氣姐姐」Jessi合作，以及JYP朴軫永和前Wonder Girls成員宣美的「師徒合體」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5343/d5343180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5343%2Fd5343180.jpg&h=7f39c6db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲KBS《歌謠大祝祭》王嘉爾和「霸氣姐姐」Jessi合作。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／KBS World）<br />\n<br />\n南韓疫情再攀高峰，不僅單日確診人數破千創新高，疫情也延燒至演藝圈。儘管多名偶像歌手和化妝師等相關工作人員陸續確診，電視台仍決定照常舉行年末活動。KBS《歌謠大祝祭》18日播出，召集包括防彈少年團、TWICE、朴軫永 X 宣美、NCT、IZ*ONE等24組藝人演出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5343/d5343183.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5343%2Fd5343183.jpg&h=f1b6c138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲KBS《歌謠大祝祭》王嘉爾和「霸氣姐姐」Jessi合作。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／KBS World）<br />\n<br />\nJackson和Jessi合體，演唱從節奏到歌詞都超霸氣的歌曲《NUNU NANA》，Jackson穿上超深V露出健壯胸膛，搭上Jessi狂野的斑馬紋裝，兩人從造型就超有氣勢。在結尾時，Jessi更撩起Jackson的下巴，超近距離接觸讓粉絲看了尖叫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5343/d5343188.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5343%2Fd5343188.jpg&h=acdcdd6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲KBS《歌謠大祝祭》朴軫永和宣美師徒合作。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／ KBS World）<br />\n<br />\n另一個話題合作舞台，當屬「師徒」JYP朴軫永和宣美。宣美曾經是Wonder Girls成員，當年Wonder Girls以《NOBODY》紅遍亞洲後，朴軫永帶著女孩們到美國打天下。雖然最後不算成功，但師徒培養出革命情感，即使成員們離開JYP娛樂，依然和朴軫永保持如父女般的良好互動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5343/d5343189.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5343%2Fd5343189.jpg&h=6076ddf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朴軫永和宣美師徒合作，讓TWICE看呆。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／ KBS World）<br />\n<br />\n在18日的《歌謠大祝祭》合作舞台中，朴軫永和宣美也重現了《NOBODY》的經典橋段。曾經是唱跳歌手的朴軫永寶刀未老，搖擺舞動時，直播留言狂刷一排：「歐巴我愛你！」帥氣演出連旗下歌手TWICE和Stray Kids都看呆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V6Q80XucEVg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV6Q80XucEVg&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=3bb894d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V6Q80XucEVg</a>"},{"pid":"986dfcd255c1bc506880752a213f4ee0e028bfd9","tid":2331204,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"7到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682c4bd197ca14d53e64dbbe49c977b3291b8a59","tid":2331204,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"986dfcd255c1bc506880752a213f4ee0e028bfd9","tid":2331204,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T14:57:46.000Z","msg":"7到笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T14:58:44.000Z","msg":"唔洗睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass